data.description: Welcome home to this exquisite 3-bedroom, 2-bath haven featuring a refreshing pool within a newly redone cage (2021). Spanning 1523 square feet, revel in modernity with a newly replaced roof (2021) and hurricane windows and slides. The interior boasts tasteful decor, elegant tile floors, and an open floor plan enhanced by a Bose surround sound system. The kitchen is a culinary delight, adorned with quartz counters, complemented by a suite of new appliances, including a refrigerator, dishwasher, and a washing machine. The home also offers convenient window treatments and a garage door opener, all updated in the past 2 years.  The outdoor oasis extends to a newly landscaped yard, enclosed by a stylish vinyl fence, providing both privacy and charm. With a generator hookup in place and monitored alarm system, your peace of mind is assured. Located in a prime spot close to shopping and restaurants, this residence blends modern amenities with comfort seamlessly. Don't miss the chance to make this dream home yours!
